  "explanation": [
    "Activity <katex>$A = A_0 (1/2)^{t/T_{1/2}}$</katex>.",
    "<katex>$1/5 = (1/2)^{t/3}$</katex>.",
    "Take log base 2: <katex>$\\log_2 5 = t/3$</katex>.",
